 auf den Weg, damit Sie den Kurerfolg so lange wie m\u00f6glich erhalten k\u00f6nnen. Unser Ern\u00e4hrungsplan hat in der Vergangenheit besonders gute Erfolge bei Patienten mit Hautkrankheiten, wie beispielsweise Akne, Neurodermitis oder Schuppenflechte, erzielt", "language": null, "image": null, "pagetype": "article", "links": ["/", "/zimmer/", "/zimmer/economy/", "/zimmer/comfort/", "/zimmer/comfort-plus/", "/zimmer/superior/", "/zimmer/superior-plus/", "/zimmer/suite/", "/zimmer/superior-suite-plus/", "/ayurveda/", "/ayurveda/ayurveda-zentrum/", "/ayurveda/ayurveda-kuren/", "/ayurveda/individuelle-ayurveda-behandlungen/", "/ayurveda/unsere-ayurveda-arzte-und-therapeuten/", "/ayurveda/ayurvedische-kuche/", "/infos-und-angebote/", "/gastronomie/", "/gastronomie/ayurveda-restaurant/", "/gastronomie/batahira-restaurant/", "/gastronomie/lobby-bar/", "/gastronomie/pool-bar/", "/korper-geist/", "/korper-geist/beauty-studio/", "/korper-geist/yoga/", "/korper-geist/meditation/", "/korper-geist/impressionen/", "/freizeit/", "/freizeit/interne-freizeitangebote/", "/freizeit/externe-freizeitangebote/", "/ausfluge/", "/nachrichten/", "https://www.lankaprincess.com", "/booking/", "https://www.facebook.com/lankaprincess", "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_ZsuQqVXbh9ZfH690rLSRA", "https://instagram.com/lankaprincess/", "javascript:void(0);", "#", "#", "#", "#", "#", "#", "#", "#", "https://www.lankaprincess.de/wp-content/uploads/Lanka-Princess-Ayurveda-Kurprogramme-01_11_2022-31_10_2023_V01.pdf", "https://www.lankaprincess.de/wp-content/uploads/Lanka-Princess-Ayurveda-Kurprogramme-01_11_2022-31_10_2023_V01.pdf", "https://www.lankaprincess.de/wp-content/uploads/Lanka-Princess-Ayurveda-Kurprogramme_01-11-2023-31-10-2024_v01.pdf", "https://www.lankaprincess.de/wp-content/uploads/Lanka-Princess-Ayurveda-Kurprogramme_01-11-2023-31-10-2024_v01.pdf", "https://www.lankaprincess.de/parkinson-treatment-18-day/", "https://www.lankaprincess.de/ayurvedisches-festtagsmenu/", "https://www.l